Lecture 15: Bioinformatics 
Sayan Mukherjee  

Description 
We discuss the machine learning challenges in bioinformatics. Some basic 
molecular biology is described. Some common bioinformatics problems 
are briefly discussed. The use of classification algorithms in the analysis 
of DNA Microarray data is discussed at length.  

  
Suggested Reading 
•  T. Golub et al Molecular Classification of Cancer: Class 
Discovery and Class Prediction by Gene Expression. Science 
1999.  
•  S. Mukherjee et al Support Vector Machine Classification of 
Microarray Data . AI Memo 1999.  
•  S. Ramaswamy et al Multiclass Cancer Diagnosis Using Tumor 
Gene Expression Signatures . PNAS 2001.  

 

 

